              "free_text": [
                " The External Target Facility (ETF) of",
                "the Heavy Ion Research Facility in Lanzhou-Cooler",
                "Storage Ring(HIRFL-CSR)"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Primary 18O beams were accelerated to 280 MeV/nucleon",
                "by HIRFL-CSR and fragmented on a 15-mm-thick Be target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "900 mg/cm2 carbon target"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EDE",
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The generated secondary beams were",
                "subsequently selected by their magnetic rigidities in",
                "the second Radioactive Ion Beam Line in Lanzhou",
                " (RIBLL2) and then delivered to ETF to impinge on a",
                "900 mg/cm2 carbon target, where their energies",
                "dropped to around 240 MeV/nucleon upon hitting the",
                "target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "IOCH",
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The particle Z number was recorded by the",
                "multisampling ionization chamber (MUSIC) downstream",
                "from the reaction target, while the particle TOF were",
                "given by the plastic scintillators and the TOF Wall."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TRD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The heavy reaction products were traced via a",
                "series of drift chambers, lined up along the",
                "particles' flying directions, with the latter",
                "constituting the multi-wire drift chamber (MWDC) Array."
              ]
            }
          ],
